<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">To understand how customers/users use our products and services, to monitor and prevent problems and issues, and to improve our products and services.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">To provide customer support, and to analyze and improve our interactions with customers/users.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">To detect and prevent fraudulent transactions and other illegal activities, to report spam, and to protect the rights and interests of Work Companion, WoCo&rsquo;s users, third parties and the public.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">To update, expand and analyze our records, identify new customers, and provide products and services that may be of interest to the customer/user;</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">To analyze trends, administer our websites, and track visitor navigations on our websites to understand what visitors are looking for and to better help them;</span></li>
</ol>
<p>&nbsp;</p>


<h3><b>Disclosure of Information for legal reasons</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Work Companion may disclose Customer&rsquo;s Personal Information if Work Companion has a good-faith belief that such disclosure is absolutely necessary to : </span></p>
