<h3><b>Security of Personal Information</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We use reasonable measures to maintain the security of Customer Personal Information. Work Companion has implemented industry-standard electronic means of protecting Customer Personal Information. We store Personal Information behind a computer firewall, a barrier designed to prevent outsiders from accessing our servers. In addition,Work Companion protects Customer Personal Information from unauthorized physical access by storing Customer Personal Information in a controlled facility. Except as provided elsewhere in this Privacy Policy, Work Companion limits access to Personal Information in electronic databases to those persons (including employees and contractors) in work Companion' organization who have a business need for such access. Even though Work Companion has taken significant steps to ensure that Customer Personal Data is not intercepted, accessed, used, or disclosed by unauthorized persons, you should know that Work Companion cannot eliminate security risks associated with Personal Data.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We secure customer information during transmission by encryption.</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>


<h3><b>Changes, Revisions and Updation of this Privacy Policy</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Work Companion may modify this Privacy Policy at any time, upon notifying you through a service announcement or by sending an email to your primary email address. If Work Companion makes significant changes to this Privacy Policy that affect your rights, you will be provided with at least 30 days' advance notice of the changes by email to your primary email address. If you think that the updated Privacy Policy affects your rights with respect to your use of our products or services, you may terminate your use by sending us an email within 30 days. Your continued use after the effective date of changes to the Privacy Policy will be deemed to be your agreement to the modified Privacy Policy. You will not receive email notification of minor changes to the Privacy Policy. If you are concerned about how your personal information is used, you should check back at https://www.woco.co.in/privacy.html periodically.</span></p>
